# World Cup 2026 Teletext Dashboard — environment variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your keys.
# .env.local is gitignored — never commit real API keys.
#
# IMPORTANT: these are SERVER-SIDE only — do NOT prefix with VITE_ (that would
# inline them into the public browser bundle). They are read by the Vite dev
# proxy (vite.config.ts) and by the Vercel serverless functions in /api.
# In production, set the same names in the Vercel project's Environment Variables.

# ── Live Scores · football-data.org ────────────────────────────────────────
# Free tier (10 req/min, major competitions incl. World Cup).
# Sign up: https://www.football-data.org/client/register
# Competition code for FIFA World Cup: WC  (season auto-set to 2026)
FD_KEY=your_football_data_org_key_here

# ── Match Preview · API-Football (api-sports.io) ───────────────────────────
# Free tier (~100 req/day). Provides line-ups, injuries, stats, predictions, odds.
# Sign up: https://www.api-football.com/
API_FOOTBALL_KEY=your_api_football_key_here

# ── News Headlines · BBC Sport RSS ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Fetched server-side via /api/rss (no key needed). No configuration required.
